description:
This skill will ask you the name of capital and you name the capital.  For example, Alexa will ask "What is the capital of United Kingdom?" and you would reply with "London".

You can start the skill by saying "Alexa, open Capital Flash Cards".
exampleInteractions: Alexa, open Capital Flash Cards and start a new game.
name: Capital Flash Cards
shortDescription: Learn the name of the capital of a country in the world.  You will be given the name of a country and you provide the name of the capital.
